# .npmrc Configuration Example
# Copy this to ~/.npmrc and replace YOUR_NPM_TOKEN with your actual npm token

# For public npm registry (npm.org)
# @davidwarshawsky:registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/

# For GitHub Package Registry
# @davidwarshawsky:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
# //npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN

# Authentication token for npm registry
# //registry.npmjs.org/:_authToken=YOUR_NPM_TOKEN

# To generate npm token:
# 1. Visit https://npmjs.com/settings/tokens
# 2. Create a new "Publish" token
# 3. Copy and use in this file

# Make sure to place the real .npmrc in your home directory:
# ~/.npmrc
